{
  "video_id": "E_fB_s_TC5k",
  "title": "Buildings that blend nature and city | Jeanne Gang",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Camille Mart√≠nez"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12734.0,
      "end_time": 14940.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a relationship builder."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14964.0,
      "end_time": 16936.0,
      "text": "When you think of a relationship builder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 16960.0,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t you just automatically think \"architect?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 19742.0,
      "end_time": 21165.0,
      "text": "Probably not."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 21897.0,
      "end_time": 26102.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because most people think architects design buildings and cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26127.0,
      "end_time": 28480.0,
      "text": "but what we really design are relationships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29203.0,
      "end_time": 31310.0,
      "text": "because cities are about people."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31334.0,
      "end_time": 34716.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re places where people come together for all kinds of exchange."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34740.0,
      "end_time": 37957.0,
      "text": "And besides, skylines are highly specific urban habitats"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37981.0,
      "end_time": 40299.0,
      "text": "with their own insects, plants and animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40323.0,
      "end_time": 41956.0,
      "text": "and even their own weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42470.0,
      "end_time": 45214.0,
      "text": "But today, urban habitats are out of balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45623.0,
      "end_time": 49655.0,
      "text": "Climate change, together with political and economic troubles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49679.0,
      "end_time": 50831.0,
      "text": "are having an impact;"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50855.0,
      "end_time": 54166.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re adding up and stressing out cities and us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54191.0,
      "end_time": 55722.0,
      "text": "the people who live in them."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56820.0,
      "end_time": 60445.0,
      "text": "For me, the field of ecology has provided important insight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60469.0,
      "end_time": 64678.0,
      "text": "because ecologists don&#39;t just look at individual species on their own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64702.0,
      "end_time": 67895.0,
      "text": "they look at the relationships between living things"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67919.0,
      "end_time": 69167.0,
      "text": "and their environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70374.0,
      "end_time": 74252.0,
      "text": "They look at how all the diverse parts of the ecosystem are interconnected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74276.0,
      "end_time": 78574.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s actually this balance, this web of life, that sustains life."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79880.0,
      "end_time": 83679.0,
      "text": "My team and I have been applying insights from ecology to architecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83704.0,
      "end_time": 87698.0,
      "text": "to see how physical space can help build stronger relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88124.0,
      "end_time": 90860.0,
      "text": "The projects I&#39;m going to show you today"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90110.0,
      "end_time": 93813.0,
      "text": "use the idea of building relationships as the key driver for design."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94672.0,
      "end_time": 96505.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s an example of what I mean."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96529.0,
      "end_time": 100678.0,
      "text": "Recently, we were asked to design a center for social justice leadership"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100702.0,
      "end_time": 102252.0,
      "text": "called the Arcus Center."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102922.0,
      "end_time": 106444.0,
      "text": "They asked us for a building that could break down traditional barriers"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106468.0,
      "end_time": 107752.0,
      "text": "between different groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107776.0,
      "end_time": 112230.0,
      "text": "and in doing so, create possibilities for meaningful conversations"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112470.0,
      "end_time": 113551.0,
      "text": "around social justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114530.0,
      "end_time": 116710.0,
      "text": "The students wanted a place for cultural exchange."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116734.0,
      "end_time": 120533.0,
      "text": "They thought a place for preparing food together could do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120557.0,
      "end_time": 123288.0,
      "text": "And they wanted to be welcoming to the outside community."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 123312.0,
      "end_time": 125975.0,
      "text": "They thought a fireplace could draw people in"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125999.0,
      "end_time": 128294.0,
      "text": "and help start conversations."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129372.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132838.0,
      "text": "And everybody wanted the work of social justice to be visible"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132862.0,
      "end_time": 134281.0,
      "text": "to the outside world."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 135388.0,
      "end_time": 138129.0,
      "text": "There really wasn&#39;t a precedent for this kind of space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138153.0,
      "end_time": 140620.0,
      "text": "so we looked around the globe and found examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 140644.0,
      "end_time": 142389.0,
      "text": "of community meeting houses."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 142794.0,
      "end_time": 144984.0,
      "text": "Community meeting houses are places"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 145800.0,
      "end_time": 148369.0,
      "text": "where there&#39;s very specific relationships between people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 148393.0,
      "end_time": 151565.0,
      "text": "like this one in Mali, where the elders gather."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152900.0,
      "end_time": 155560.0,
      "text": "The low roof keeps everybody seated and at equal eye level."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 155585.0,
      "end_time": 156808.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very egalitarian."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 156832.0,
      "end_time": 159310.0,
      "text": "I mean, you can&#39;t stand up and take over the meeting."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159334.0,
      "end_time": 160847.0,
      "text": "You&#39;d actually bump your head."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 160871.0,
      "end_time": 162524.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 162548.0,
      "end_time": 165162.0,
      "text": "In meeting houses, there&#39;s always a central space"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 165186.0,
      "end_time": 167837.0,
      "text": "where you can sit around a circle and see each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 167861.0,
      "end_time": 169881.0,
      "text": "So we designed a space just like that"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 169906.0,
      "end_time": 171885.0,
      "text": "right in the middle of the Arcus Center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 171909.0,
      "end_time": 174899.0,
      "text": "and we anchored it with a fireplace and a kitchen."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174923.0,
      "end_time": 178395.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s pretty hard to get a kitchen and a fireplace in a building like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 178419.0,
      "end_time": 179623.0,
      "text": "with the building codes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 179647.0,
      "end_time": 182448.0,
      "text": "but it was so important to the concept, we got it done."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 183108.0,
      "end_time": 186889.0,
      "text": "And now the central space works for big social gatherings"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186913.0,
      "end_time": 190151.0,
      "text": "and a place to meet one-on-one for the very first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 190175.0,
      "end_time": 192254.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s almost like this three-way intersection"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 192278.0,
      "end_time": 195852.0,
      "text": "that encourages bumping into people and starting a conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 196496.0,
      "end_time": 199640.0,
      "text": "Now you can always pass the kitchen and see something going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 199664.0,
      "end_time": 203110.0,
      "text": "You can sit by the fireplace and share stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 203574.0,
      "end_time": 206771.0,
      "text": "You can study together in big groups or in small ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 206795.0,
      "end_time": 210310.0,
      "text": "because the architecture sets up these opportunities."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 211461.0,
      "end_time": 214640.0,
      "text": "Even the construction is about building relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 214880.0,
      "end_time": 215948.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s made of cordwood masonry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 215973.0,
      "end_time": 218910.0,
      "text": "which is using logs the way you would use bricks."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 218934.0,
      "end_time": 221905.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s super low-tech and easy to do and anyone can do it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 221929.0,
      "end_time": 223606.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the entire point."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 223630.0,
      "end_time": 226597.0,
      "text": "The act of making is a social activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 228232.0,
      "end_time": 230240.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s good for the planet, too:"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 230264.0,
      "end_time": 233360.0,
      "text": "the trees absorbed carbon when they were growing up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 233384.0,
      "end_time": 235280.0,
      "text": "and they gave off oxygen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 235520.0,
      "end_time": 237793.0,
      "text": "and now that carbon is trapped inside the walls"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 237817.0,
      "end_time": 240990.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s not being released into the atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 241140.0,
      "end_time": 245850.0,
      "text": "So making the walls is equivalent to taking cars right off the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 245969.0,
      "end_time": 248238.0,
      "text": "We chose the building method"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 248262.0,
      "end_time": 252208.0,
      "text": "because it connects people to each other and to the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 253255.0,
      "end_time": 254406.0,
      "text": "But is it working?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 254430.0,
      "end_time": 256696.0,
      "text": "Is it creating relationships and nurturing them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 256720.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258380.00000000003,
      "text": "How can we know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 258620.0,
      "end_time": 261473.0,
      "text": "Well, more and more people are coming here, for one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 261497.0,
      "end_time": 263817.0,
      "text": "and as a result of the fireside chats"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 263841.0,
      "end_time": 265939.0,
      "text": "and a full calendar of programming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 265963.0,
      "end_time": 268551.0,
      "text": "people are applying for the Arcus Fellowships."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 268575.0,
      "end_time": 272873.0,
      "text": "In fact, applications have increased tenfold for the Arcus Fellowship"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 272898.0,
      "end_time": 274163.0,
      "text": "since the building opened."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 274187.0,
      "end_time": 276857.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s working. It&#39;s bringing people together."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 278740.0,
      "end_time": 280442.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve shown how architecture can connect people"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 280466.0,
      "end_time": 282624.0,
      "text": "on this kind of horizontal campus scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 283165.0,
      "end_time": 286663.0,
      "text": "But we wondered if social relationships could be scaled up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 286687.0,
      "end_time": 289340.0,
      "text": "or rather, upward -- in tall buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 290201.0,
      "end_time": 294238.0,
      "text": "Tall buildings don&#39;t necessarily lend themselves to being social buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 294262.0,
      "end_time": 296255.0,
      "text": "They can seem isolating and inward."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 296646.0,
      "end_time": 301178.0,
      "text": "You might only see people in those awkward elevator rides."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 302496.0,
      "end_time": 306700.0,
      "text": "But in several major cities, I&#39;ve been designing tall buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 306310.0,
      "end_time": 309372.0,
      "text": "that are based on creating relationships between people."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 309396.0,
      "end_time": 310872.0,
      "text": "This is Aqua."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 310896.0,
      "end_time": 314470.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a residential high-rise in Chicago"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 314494.0,
      "end_time": 317105.0,
      "text": "aimed at young urban professionals and empty nesters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 317129.0,
      "end_time": 318772.0,
      "text": "many of them new to the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 319637.0,
      "end_time": 323563.0,
      "text": "With over 700 apartments, we wanted to see if we could use architecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 323587.0,
      "end_time": 325658.0,
      "text": "to help people get to know their neighbors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 325682.0,
      "end_time": 328932.0,
      "text": "even when their homes are organized in the vertical dimension."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 330908.0,
      "end_time": 334624.0,
      "text": "So we invented a way to use balconies as the new social connectors."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 335389.0,
      "end_time": 338929.0,
      "text": "The shapes of the floor slabs vary slightly and they transition"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 338953.0,
      "end_time": 340322.0,
      "text": "as you go up the tower."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 340346.0,
      "end_time": 344247.0,
      "text": "The result of this is that you can actually see people"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 344271.0,
      "end_time": 345616.0,
      "text": "from your balcony."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 345640.0,
      "end_time": 347772.0,
      "text": "The balconies are misregistered."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 347797.0,
      "end_time": 349941.0,
      "text": "You can lean over your balcony and say, \"Hey!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 349965.0,
      "end_time": 352166.0,
      "text": "just like you would across the backyard."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 352967.0,
      "end_time": 354846.0,
      "text": "To make the balconies more comfortable"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 354870.0,
      "end_time": 357147.0,
      "text": "for a longer period of time during the year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 357171.0,
      "end_time": 359637.0,
      "text": "we studied the wind with digital simulations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 359661.0,
      "end_time": 362523.0,
      "text": "so the effect of the balcony shapes breaks up the wind"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 362547.0,
      "end_time": 363858.0,
      "text": "and confuses the wind"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 363882.0,
      "end_time": 366939.0,
      "text": "and makes the balconies more comfortable and less windy."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 367930.0,
      "end_time": 370879.0,
      "text": "Now, just by being able to go outside on your balcony"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 370903.0,
      "end_time": 372978.0,
      "text": "or on the third floor roof terrace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 373200.0,
      "end_time": 375870.0,
      "text": "you can be connected to the outdoors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 375111.0,
      "end_time": 377241.0,
      "text": "even when you&#39;re way above the ground plane."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 377266.0,
      "end_time": 380100.0,
      "text": "So the building acts to create community"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 380250.0,
      "end_time": 382645.0,
      "text": "within the building and the city at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 382670.0,
      "end_time": 383836.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s working."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 384683.0,
      "end_time": 388683.0,
      "text": "And people are starting to meet each other on the building surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 388707.0,
      "end_time": 389863.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ve heard --"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 389887.0,
      "end_time": 390943.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 390967.0,
      "end_time": 393734.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve even starting getting together as couples."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 394576.0,
      "end_time": 397203.0,
      "text": "But besides romantic relationships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 397227.0,
      "end_time": 399467.0,
      "text": "the building has a positive social effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 399491.0,
      "end_time": 401428.0,
      "text": "on the community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 401452.0,
      "end_time": 404139.0,
      "text": "as evidenced by people starting groups together"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 404163.0,
      "end_time": 406900.0,
      "text": "and starting big projects together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 406330.0,
      "end_time": 410900.0,
      "text": "like this organic community garden on the building&#39;s roof terrace."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 411694.0,
      "end_time": 414710.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve shown how tall buildings can be social connectors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 414734.0,
      "end_time": 416726.0,
      "text": "but what about public architecture?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 416750.0,
      "end_time": 420613.0,
      "text": "How can we create better social cohesion in public buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 420637.0,
      "end_time": 421994.0,
      "text": "and civic spaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 422180.0,
      "end_time": 423450.0,
      "text": "and why is it important?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 423890.0,
      "end_time": 425986.0,
      "text": "Public architecture is just not as successful"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 426110.0,
      "end_time": 427935.0,
      "text": "if it comes from the top down."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 429313.0,
      "end_time": 431411.0,
      "text": "About 15 years ago in Chicago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 431435.0,
      "end_time": 434542.0,
      "text": "they started to replace old police stations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 434566.0,
      "end_time": 437736.0,
      "text": "and they built this identical model all over the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 438319.0,
      "end_time": 440880.0,
      "text": "And even though they had good intentions"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 440904.0,
      "end_time": 443402.0,
      "text": "of treating all neighborhoods equally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 443426.0,
      "end_time": 445846.0,
      "text": "the communities didn&#39;t feel invested in the process"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 445870.0,
      "end_time": 448384.0,
      "text": "or feel a sense of ownership of these buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 448408.0,
      "end_time": 451935.0,
      "text": "It was equality in the sense that everybody gets the same police station,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 451959.0,
      "end_time": 455313.0,
      "text": "but it wasn&#39;t equity in the sense of responding"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 455337.0,
      "end_time": 457695.0,
      "text": "to each community&#39;s individual needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 457719.0,
      "end_time": 460560.0,
      "text": "And equity is the key issue here."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 460584.0,
      "end_time": 463984.0,
      "text": "You know, in my field, there&#39;s a debate"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 464800.0,
      "end_time": 466599.0,
      "text": "about whether architecture can even do anything"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 466623.0,
      "end_time": 468808.0,
      "text": "to improve social relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 468832.0,
      "end_time": 474266.0,
      "text": "But I believe that we need architecture and every tool in our tool kit"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 474290.0,
      "end_time": 476228.0,
      "text": "to improve these relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 477133.0,
      "end_time": 480515.0,
      "text": "In the US, policy reforms have been recommended"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 480540.0,
      "end_time": 482344.0,
      "text": "in order to rebuild trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 482368.0,
      "end_time": 483776.0,
      "text": "But my team and I wondered"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 483800.0,
      "end_time": 486839.0,
      "text": "if design and a more inclusive design process"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 486863.0,
      "end_time": 490516.0,
      "text": "could help add something positive to this policy conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 490540.0,
      "end_time": 492226.0,
      "text": "We asked ourselves simply:"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 492250.0,
      "end_time": 494206.0,
      "text": "Can design help rebuild trust?"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 494928.0,
      "end_time": 499250.0,
      "text": "So we reached out to community members and police officers in North Lawndale;"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 499274.0,
      "end_time": 500833.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a neighborhood in Chicago"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 500857.0,
      "end_time": 503673.0,
      "text": "where the police station is perceived as a scary fortress"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 503697.0,
      "end_time": 505386.0,
      "text": "surrounded by a parking lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 506740.0,
      "end_time": 508692.0,
      "text": "In North Lawndale, people are afraid of police"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 508716.0,
      "end_time": 510921.0,
      "text": "and of going anywhere near the police station,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 510945.0,
      "end_time": 512232.0,
      "text": "even to report a crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 512663.0,
      "end_time": 515416.0,
      "text": "So we organized this brainstorming session"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 515440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517980.00000000006,
      "text": "with both groups participating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 517121.0,
      "end_time": 520301.0,
      "text": "and we came up with this whole new idea for the police station."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 520961.0,
      "end_time": 522866.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called \"Polis Station.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 522890.0,
      "end_time": 527610.0,
      "text": "\"Polis\" is a Greek word that means a place with a sense of community."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 528348.0,
      "end_time": 529968.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s based on the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 529992.0,
      "end_time": 533929.0,
      "text": "that if you can increase opportunities for positive social interactions"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 533953.0,
      "end_time": 536246.0,
      "text": "between police and community members,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 536270.0,
      "end_time": 538465.0,
      "text": "you can rebuild that relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 538489.0,
      "end_time": 541203.0,
      "text": "and activate the neighborhood at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 542300.0,
      "end_time": 545108.0,
      "text": "Instead of the police station as a scary fortress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 545132.0,
      "end_time": 549589.0,
      "text": "you get highly active spaces on the public side of the station --"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 549613.0,
      "end_time": 551123.0,
      "text": "places that spark conversation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 551147.0,
      "end_time": 553707.0,
      "text": "like a barbershop, a coffee shop"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 553731.0,
      "end_time": 555304.0,
      "text": "or sports courts as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 555328.0,
      "end_time": 557507.0,
      "text": "Both cops and kids said they love sports."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 558159.0,
      "end_time": 561550.0,
      "text": "These insights came directly from the community members"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 561574.0,
      "end_time": 563906.0,
      "text": "and the police officers themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 563930.0,
      "end_time": 567689.0,
      "text": "and as designers, our role was just to connect the dots"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 567713.0,
      "end_time": 569334.0,
      "text": "and suggest the first step."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 569673.0,
      "end_time": 572287.0,
      "text": "So with the help of the city and the parks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 572311.0,
      "end_time": 576597.0,
      "text": "we were able to raise funds and design and build a half-court,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 576621.0,
      "end_time": 578961.0,
      "text": "right on the police station parking lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 578985.0,
      "end_time": 580426.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a start."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 580450.0,
      "end_time": 582318.0,
      "text": "But is it rebuilding trust?"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 582674.0,
      "end_time": 586250.0,
      "text": "The people in North Lawndale say the kids are using the courts every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 586274.0,
      "end_time": 589623.0,
      "text": "and they even organize tournaments like this one shown here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 589647.0,
      "end_time": 592261.0,
      "text": "and once in a while an officer joins in."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 594840.0,
      "end_time": 596750.0,
      "text": "But now, they even have basketballs inside the station"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 596774.0,
      "end_time": 598390.0,
      "text": "that kids can borrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 598630.0,
      "end_time": 600555.0,
      "text": "And recently they&#39;ve asked us to expand the courts"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 600579.0,
      "end_time": 602521.0,
      "text": "and build a park on the site."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 604459.0,
      "end_time": 606827.0,
      "text": "And parents report something astonishing."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 607311.0,
      "end_time": 611542.0,
      "text": "Before, there was fear of going anywhere the station, and now they say"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 611566.0,
      "end_time": 615530.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a sense that the court is safer than other courts nearby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 615770.0,
      "end_time": 617351.0,
      "text": "and they prefer their kids to play here."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 618970.0,
      "end_time": 619687.0,
      "text": "So maybe in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 619711.0,
      "end_time": 621357.0,
      "text": "on the public side of the station,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 621381.0,
      "end_time": 625860.0,
      "text": "you might be able to drop in for a haircut at the barbershop"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 625110.0,
      "end_time": 627759.0,
      "text": "or reserve the community room for a birthday party"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 627783.0,
      "end_time": 629426.0,
      "text": "or renew your driver&#39;s license"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 629450.0,
      "end_time": 631548.0,
      "text": "or get money out of an ATM."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 632240.0,
      "end_time": 634715.0,
      "text": "It can be a place for neighbors to meet each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 634739.0,
      "end_time": 637426.0,
      "text": "and to get to know the officers, and vice versa."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 638601.0,
      "end_time": 640545.0,
      "text": "This is not a utopian fantasy."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 640569.0,
      "end_time": 644557.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about how do you design to rebuild trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 644581.0,
      "end_time": 646680.0,
      "text": "trusting relationships?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 646829.0,
      "end_time": 650620.0,
      "text": "You know, every city has parks, libraries, schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 650644.0,
      "end_time": 652380.0,
      "text": "and other public buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 652620.0,
      "end_time": 656248.0,
      "text": "that have the potential to be reimagined as social connectors."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 656954.0,
      "end_time": 660983.0,
      "text": "But reimagining the buildings for the future is going to require"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 661800.0,
      "end_time": 663116.0,
      "text": "engaging the people who live there."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 663799.0,
      "end_time": 667687.0,
      "text": "Engaging the public can be intimidating, and I&#39;ve felt that, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 667711.0,
      "end_time": 669992.0,
      "text": "But maybe that&#39;s because in architecture school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 670160.0,
      "end_time": 674220.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t really learn how to engage the public in the act of design."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 674470.0,
      "end_time": 677157.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re taught to defend our design against criticism."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 677594.0,
      "end_time": 679662.0,
      "text": "But I think that can change, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 680813.0,
      "end_time": 683386.0,
      "text": "So if we can focus the design mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 683410.0,
      "end_time": 687390.0,
      "text": "on creating positive, reinforcing relationships"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 687414.0,
      "end_time": 689394.0,
      "text": "in architecture and through architecture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 689418.0,
      "end_time": 693284.0,
      "text": "I believe we can do much more than create individual buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 694650.0,
      "end_time": 697260.0,
      "text": "We can reduce the stress and the polarization"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 697284.0,
      "end_time": 698848.0,
      "text": "in our urban habitats."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 700100.0,
      "end_time": 701965.0,
      "text": "We can create relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 701989.0,
      "end_time": 704788.0,
      "text": "We can help steady this planet we all share."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 705962.0,
      "end_time": 707121.0,
      "text": "See?"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 707145.0,
      "end_time": 709384.0,
      "text": "Architects really are relationship builders."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 709408.0,
      "end_time": 710770.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 710794.0,
      "end_time": 711946.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 711970.0,
      "end_time": 714150.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}